{title: 你的同在}
{title_pinyin: Nǐ de tóng zài}
{artist: Robert & Lea Sutanto}
{key: D}
{tempo: 67}
{language: zh}

{start_of_intro: 前奏/Intro}
[D]  [Bm]  [C#m7(b5)]  [F#7]  [Bm7]  [E7]  [A7]
[D]  [Bm]  [C#m7(b5)]  [F#7]  [Bm]  [E7]  [A7]
